init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A man is speaking to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a film director, and he has a movie he wants to make.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't remember agreeing to make a movie of my next life," you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Therefore, you don't remember making the movie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "It is your future," says the man, "but it is also your past.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "It is a paradox," says the man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "No, no," says the man, "it is not a scam.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You mean you don't know whether it is a scam or not?" you ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "But you are the director," you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I am the director," says the man, "but I don't remember making this movie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes," says the man, "I am an idiot."
